\c 16
\s Jobho anochema njodzi yaanopiwa naMwari
\p
\v 1 Zvino Jobho wakapindura, ndokuti:
\p
\v 2 Ndanzwa zvinhu zvizhinji zvakadai\x + 12.3.\x*; vanyaradzi vanotambudza imwi mese\x + 13.4.\x*.
\v 3 Mashoko ano\add ngo\add*va mhepo ane mugumo here? Kana chii chinokurwarisai kuti mupindure\x + 6.25.\x*?
\v 4 Neniwo ndaitaura semwi kana mweya wenyu waiva pachinzvimbo chemweya wangu; ndaiunganidzawo mashoko pamusoro penyu, nekukudzungudzirai musoro wangu\x + Jer. 18.16. Mat. 27.39. 2 Madz. 19.21.\x*.
\v 5 Ndingadai ndaikusimbisai nemuromo wangu, uye kufamba kwemiromo yangu kwaitapudza\x + 16.6.\x* \add marwadzo enyu\add*.
\v 6 Kunyange ndichitaura, marwadzo angu haatapudzwi; kana ndichirega, chii chinobva kwandiri?
\v 7 Asi ikozvino iye wandinetesa; iwe waparadza ungano yangu yose\x + 15.34. 1.15-19.\x*.
\v 8 Imwi mandiunyanisa\x + 2.7. 16.15.\x*, huve uchapupu\x + 10.17.\x*; uye kuonda kwangu\x + 2.7. 16.15.\x* kwandimukira\x + Map. 109.24.\x*; kunopupura pachiso changu.
\p
\v 9 Kutsamwa kwake kunobvambura\x + 10.16. 18.4. Hos. 6.1. Amo. 1.11.\x*, uye anondivenga\x + 30.21. Gen.. 27.41.\x*; anondigedera mazino ake\x + Map. 35.16. 37.12. Map. 112.10. Marir. 2.16.\x*; muvengi wangu anondirodzera meso ake\x + Map. 7.12.\x*.
\v 10 Vakandishamisira muromo wavo\x + 29.23. Map. 22.13. Isa. 5.14.\x*; mukunyomba vakarova dama rangu\x + Marir. 3.30. Isa. 50.6. 1 Madz. 22.24.\x*; vanoungana pamwe kundirwisa.
\v 11 Mwari anondipa kune vasakarurama\x + 19.18.\x*, nekundikanda pamaoko evakaipa\x + Num.. 22.32.\x*.
\v 12 Ndaiva pakuzorora, asi iye wakandivhuna\x + Isa. 24.19.\x*; akandibata nemutsipa, ndokundiputsanya\x + Jer. 23.29.\x*; akandimisa kuva chinangwa chemupotseri chake\x + 7.20. Marir. 3.12.\x*.
\v 13 Vafuri vemiseve vake vanondikomba\x + 6.4. Jer. 50.29.\x*; anopamura itsvo dzangu, uye haaregi; anodurura nduru yangu pasi\x + Marir. 2.11.\x*.
\v 14 Anondikoromora nekukoromora pamusoro pekukoromora; anomhanyira kwandiri seane simba\x + 30.14.\x*.
\p
\v 15 Ndakasonera masaga\x + 1 Madz. 20.31.\x* paganda rangu\x + 2.7. 16.15.\x*; ndakaroverera runyanga rwangu muguruva\x + Map. 75.10.\x*.
\v 16 Chiso changu chitsvuku nekuchema\x + Marir. 1.20. 2.11.\x*, uye pazvidziviro zvemeso zvangu pane mumvuri werufu\x + 3.5.\x*.
\v 17 Kunyange pasina chikuriri pamaoko angu, uye munyengetero wangu wakachena\x + Isa. 53.9.\x*.
\p
\v 18 Nyika, rega kufukidza ropa rangu\x + Isa. 26.21. Eze. 24.7.\x*; uye kuchema kwangu ngakusava nenzvimbo\x + Gen.. 4.10.\x*.
\v 19 Naikozvino, tarirai, chapupu changu chiri kumatenga, uye mupupuri wangu ari panzvimbo dzakakwirira\x + Map. 89.37.\x*.
\v 20 Shamwari dzangu vanyombi vangu; ziso rangu rinodonhedzera kuna Mwari.
\v 21 Dai kwaiva neanokumbirira munhu kuna Mwari, semwanakomana wemunhu kune wekwake\x + 9.33.\x*.
\v 22 Nokuti makore mashoma achasvika, uye ndichafamba nzira yandisingazodzoki \add nayo\add*.